cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image classification and segmentation using neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of MLP and CNN also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also deals with information retrieval from medical images, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the use of wireless capsule endoscopy suggests the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
